# important

1.	no dependencies
2.	reasonable compatibility
3.	fixed header support
4.	works on jump-links with minimal config (0-5 lines)
5.	can be used from javascript
6.	small
7.	uses requestAnimationFrame
8.	usable packaging
9.	horizontal support
10.	standards complient
11.	active
12.	supports containers other than full page
13.	change direction mid-scroll
14.	keeps history intact

